<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She's currently starring in a Cabaret show at London's Proud Embankment.</p>

<p>And Denise Van Outen put on a racy display in a sequin-adorned bustier, fishnet tights and a top hat as she shared an pre-show snap on Saturday.</p>

<p>The West End star, 46, looked confident as she posed up a storm for the Instagram post. </p>

<p>Wow! Denise Van Outen flaunted her pins in fishnets and a black sequin bustier as she shared a sexy snap ahead of her Cabaret show on Saturday</p>

<p>The number had a sequin tassel belt, while the bustier was covered in silver glitter and an embroidered red rose.</p>

