<p>Clearly excited to be back on the stage she captioned the sexy post: 'Looking forward to performing tonight!'</p>

<p>Sultry: The number had a sequin tassel belt, while the bustier was covered in silver glitter and an embroidered red rose</p>

<p>The star recently returned to host her Cabaret show after it had to be postponed due to coronavirus.  </p>

<p>And it seems as though her talents have caught the eye of ITV bosses because she has reportedly signed up to the next series of Dancing On Ice. </p>

